{"id":8224,"date":"2021-10-31T09:49:38","date_gmt":"2021-10-31T02:49:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=8224"},"modified":"2023-10-24T17:14:26","modified_gmt":"2023-10-24T10:14:26","slug":"su-tac-dong-cua-dai-lo-dong-tay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/su-tac-dong-cua-dai-lo-dong-tay-den-gia-tri-bds-khu-vuc\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb H.B\u00ecnh Ch\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ebfn Q.2 (TP.HCM), \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 V\u00f5 V\u0103n Ki\u1ec7t &#8211; Mai Ch\u00ed Th\u1ecd (<strong>\u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y<\/strong>) c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u201cd\u00e0i 300 n\u0103m\u201d, b\u1edfi tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y d\u1ecdc xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t qua nhi\u1ec1u v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n &#8211; TP.HCM.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8277\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8277\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8277 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/cau-chuyen-ve-dai-lo-dai-300-nam-o-tphcm-1102.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/532;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8277\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8277\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/cau-chuyen-ve-dai-lo-dai-300-nam-o-tphcm-1102.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8277\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S trong khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <strong>Vinhome Land<\/strong> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u2013 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng di s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/vinhomes-grand-park\/\"><strong>C\u0103n h\u1ed9 Vinhomes Grand Park<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u2013 Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i theo chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 300 n\u0103m<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y, V\u00f5 V\u0103n Ki\u1ec7t \u2013 Mai Ch\u00ed Th\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u201cd\u00e0i 300 n\u0103m\u201d.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8276\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8276\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8276 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/ben-binh-dong-truoc-1975-2-resize-skew-jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u2013 Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng dai 300 n\u0103m\" width=\"800\" height=\"476\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/476;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8276\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8276\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/ben-binh-dong-truoc-1975-2-resize-skew-jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u2013 Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng dai 300 n\u0103m\" width=\"800\" height=\"476\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8276\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u2013 Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng dai 300 n\u0103m<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngu\u1ed3n v\u1ed1n ODA \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00ean c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch v\u00e0 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 v\u1edbi kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng di d\u1eddi r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p khu nh\u00e0 \u1ed5 chu\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9ng nh\u00e2n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed &#8211; \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i di d\u1eddi tr\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi 10.000 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan v\u00e0 h\u1ed9 d\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9, gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i hay\u00a0 tranh ch\u1ea5p n\u00e0o l\u1edbn<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ea7m Th\u1ee7 Thi\u00eam l\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1n quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y. H\u1ea7m Th\u1ee7 Thi\u00eam c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 1.5 km (1.490m) n\u1eb1m s\u00e2u d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00f2ng s\u00f4ng SaiGon, bao g\u1ed3m 2 \u0111o\u1ea1n h\u1ea7m d\u1eabn ph\u00eda Q.1 (d\u00e0i 585m), ph\u00eda Th\u1ee7 Thi\u00eam (535m) v\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1n h\u1ea7m d\u00ecm (370m). T\u1ed5ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a g\u00f3i th\u1ea7u h\u1ea7m Th\u1ee7 Thi\u00eam l\u00e0 2.083 t\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0i to\u00e1n l\u01b0u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe c\u1ed9 l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng m\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh quan m\u1eb7t n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1edd k\u00eanh d\u1ecdc theo k\u00eanh T\u00e0u H\u1ee7 \u2013 B\u1ebfn Ngh\u00e9, t\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y kinh t\u1ebf x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1eebng l\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c \u201c\u1ed5 chu\u1ed9t\u201d.\u00a0<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8286\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8286\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8286 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/thumb-phes-jpg.jpg\" alt=\"N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p khu \u1ed5 chu\u1ed9t quanh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y\" width=\"800\" height=\"351\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/351;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8286\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8286\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/thumb-phes-jpg.jpg\" alt=\"N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p khu \u1ed5 chu\u1ed9t quanh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y\" width=\"800\" height=\"351\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8286\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p khu \u1ed5 chu\u1ed9t quanh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng sau d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, TP \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tri\u1ec3n khai v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 m\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. \u201cQuan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f3 l\u00fac l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1.500 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c\u201d, theo \u00f4ng L\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u2013 X\u00f3a b\u1ecf khu \u1ed5 chu\u1ed9t xung quanh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/grand-marina-sai-gon-ba-son-quan-1\/\"><strong>C\u0103n h\u1ed9 Grand Marina Saigon<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0 xung quanh<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i to\u00e0n tuy\u1ebfn l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 23 km k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb n\u00fat giao C\u00e1t L\u00e1i \u2013 Q2 \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a0 H.B\u00ecnh Ch\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9ng nh\u00e2n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, m\u1ed9t n\u00e9t son c\u1ee7a TP.HCM v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8278 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dai-lo-vo-van-kiet-nang-cao-gia-tri.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"457\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/457;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8278\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dai-lo-vo-van-kiet-nang-cao-gia-tri.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"457\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y \u0111i qua 4 K\u0110T v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a 8 qu\u1eadn, huy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9, \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t. T\u1eeb t\u00e2y sang \u0111\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 K\u0110T m\u1edbi Th\u1ee7 Thi\u00eam n\u1eb1m \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c Q2, di chuy\u1ec3n qua h\u1ea7m Th\u1ee7 Thi\u00eam l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh Q1. Xu\u00f4i v\u1ec1 khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00eda t\u00e2y l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m kinh doanh, bu\u00f4n b\u00e1n mang b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hoa \u1edf Q5 v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh quan kh\u00f4ng gian s\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp kinh doanh s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t \u1edf Q6 v\u00e0 Q8.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap r\u00fat ng\u1eafn chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng t\u1eeb t\u00e2y sang \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a TP, \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 c\u00f2n \u0111i qua v\u1edbi 13 c\u00e2y c\u1ea7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2y c\u1ea7u b\u1eafc ngang theo tr\u1ee5c b\u1eafc nam \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong s\u1ef1 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t ph\u00eda nam TP.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ecbu s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng \u2013 T\u00e2y\u00a0<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng t\u1eeb khi \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S trong khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. V\u1edbi qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea5t d\u1ecdc theo tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u N\u0110T B\u0110S trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8287\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8287\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8287 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/unnamed-24.jpg\" alt=\"D\u1ef1 \u00e1n xung quanh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9\" width=\"800\" height=\"383\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/383;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8287\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8287\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/unnamed-24.jpg\" alt=\"D\u1ef1 \u00e1n xung quanh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9\" width=\"800\" height=\"383\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8287\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n xung quanh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n B\u0110S l\u1edbn tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u0111\u1ecba \u1ed1c, nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u00e1n B\u0110S nhanh ch\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, t\u1eeb quy ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho khu v\u1ef1c tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i theo \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh v\u00e0 khang trang h\u01a1n, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cth\u1ecfi nam ch\u00e2m\u201d thu h\u00fat d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. Nhi\u1ec1u N\u0110T v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e2y mua nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 an c\u01b0.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cBi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 B\u0110S t\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y giao \u0111\u1ed9ng kho\u1ea3ng 10 \u2013 25%\/n\u0103m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c t\u0103ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 doanh nghi\u1ec7p B\u0110S, \u0111\u1ecba \u1ed1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c N\u0110T.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8288 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/z249540622676056e11d3b6888ce52dc69d34dfa66734a-16212270511901737003413.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8288\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/z249540622676056e11d3b6888ce52dc69d34dfa66734a-16212270511901737003413.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, Vietcomreal \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Viva Riverside v\u1edbi quy m\u00f4 2 t\u00f2a th\u00e1p c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 25 t\u1ea7ng, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 trong quy m\u00f4 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi h\u01a1n 600 c\u0103n v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n giao. T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Novaland l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean tr\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, b\u00e0n giao cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0o \u1edf.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Nam Long c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Akari City t\u1ea1i Q.B\u00ecnh T\u00e2n, hay h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 3 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0 cao c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a CTY 577 v\u1edbi tr\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi 5.000 c\u0103n h\u1ed9. Ngo\u00e0i ra, CTY \u0110\u1ecba \u1ed1c Ph\u00fa Long c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang tri\u1ec3n khai x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, CTY LDG Group c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u1ef1 \u00e1n B\u0110S t\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8282\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8282\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8282 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/mai-chi-tho-3-16200299629371951374697-16212359713981912831710.jpg\" alt=\"Khu c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Viva Reverside b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8282\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8282\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/mai-chi-tho-3-16200299629371951374697-16212359713981912831710.jpg\" alt=\"Khu c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Viva Reverside b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8282\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Khu c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Viva Reverside b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n CHCC xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n quanh \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y, di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a TP H\u1ed2 CH\u00cd MINH \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd,c\u00e0ng g\u1ea7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec gi\u00e1 B\u0110S c\u00e0ng cao. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng ho\u1eb7c t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n v\u00f4 gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ebfm hoi. B\u0110S \u1edf nh\u1eefng h\u1ebbm ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u0169ng theo \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00d4NG T\u00c2Y l\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa \u0110\u00f4ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 qu\u1eadn 1, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1ef7 USD v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a qu\u1eadn 2:\u00a0<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb Sala \u0110\u1ea1i Quang Minh<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9 NEW CITY<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n NOVALAND The Sun Avenue<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 Thi\u00eam Center 86 t\u1ea7ng, Lake View Novaland<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gem Riverside<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Palm Garden, \u0110\u1ea3o Kim C\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8285 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/pxl20210511105754388-16208244859441823418336.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8285\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/pxl20210511105754388-16208244859441823418336.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u201c\u0111\u1ed1t\u201d r\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf TP HCM m\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4\u2026<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi k\u1ebft! Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\"><strong>vinhomeland.com.vn<\/strong><\/a>, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1<strong> \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c xung quanh. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 hay kh\u00f4ng. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;8224&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (1 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;S\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9 \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c\u00a0&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;118&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"3\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\